\ Words tested in this file are:
\     2CONSTANT 2LITERAL 2VARIABLE D+ D- D. D.R D0< D0= D2* D2/
\     D< D= D>S DABS DMAX DMIN DNEGATE M*/ M+ 2ROT DU<
